Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens in Amerika Justus Bier" addressed (inside) to "Herrn Professor Dr. Hans Gerhard Evers 6101 Traisa Waldstr. 43" and dated 29.05.1973

- List of works by Rubens in the North Carolina Museum of Art

- Correspondence with Justus Bier dated 1967
- Business card of Jean Neger
